### El Fin de las "Personas" Basadas en Suposiciones
* **Señal Técnica:** Integración de flujos de trabajo con Claude (IA) utilizando exclusivamente *Actual Data* (demografía, comportamiento web, consumo de medios) en lugar de "Buyer Personas" teóricos.
* **Contenido Crudo:**
> Two things marketers are obsessed with in Q1:
> A) Claude
> B) Personas
> 
> First one, obvious. And while I haven't been the biggest fan of the latter, I get why folks like 'em. Permit me this one nudge, though: please use **actual data** to inform your personas. Y'know, things like demographics, behaviors, website-visitation, what they read, watch, follow, listen-to, all the good stuff.
> 
> In fact, why not combine these two obsessions into one great taste, with a little help from your fav friends in audience research.

